               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="16r">1v-16r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s23IHA">قران, Sixteenth ǧuz’ (16/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>قَالَ أَلَمْ أَقُلْ لِّكَ (هكذا) إِنَّكَ لَنْ تَسْتَطِيْعَ مَعِيْ صَبْرَاً</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#16r">-16r</locus>ُقُلْ كُلٌ مُتَرَبِصٌ (هكذا) فَتَرَبَصُوْا (هكذا) فَسَتَعْلَمُوْنَ مِنْ أَصَحَابُ الصِرَاطِ السَوِيِ (هكذا) وَمَنْ اهْتَدَيْ</explicit>
                     <note>18:75-20:135. Title of suras rubricated. Red commas as verse markers. Twelve lines a page. Ihmāl marks (rā’-s). Vowels with a thinner qalam, sometimes difficult to catch, forgotten šadda-s. Deletions (3r, 8v) and corrections by the copyist (5r, 9r). Catchwords by another hand, pale ink. In the margins, mark of ǧuz’ in red color (1v), and mark of saǧda in black (7r).</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
